        <description>走高端路線，販售精緻設計師款包包與服飾，品質好但定價較高，購買前請確認退換貨政策。</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1684-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.1614953,-8.6841477,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[Seminyak Gallery - Bali Arts & Crafts]]></name>
        <description>峇里島手工藝品、傳統服飾、木製品一應俱全，品質比一般攤位好，適合挑選有品味的紀念品。</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1684-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.1572105,-8.682587,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Kayu Aya Square Market</name>
        <description>約30個攤位，販售服飾、捕夢網、木雕、太陽眼鏡等，開放式市集氛圍濃厚，記得砍價！建議出價不超過標價的30%。</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1684-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.1561829,-8.6859085,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>The Flea Market</name>
        <description>觀光客最常來的跳蚤市場，紗籠、藤編包、手工飾品種類豐富，賣家親切，可大膽議價，有時可壓到標價的1/3。</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1684-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.1561591,-8.6862313,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Seminyak Markets</name>
        <description>街邊露天市集，服飾、紀念品為主，貨品與其他市集類似，適合搭配逛街順路走走。</description>
